{"type":"article_comment","id":398475,"parentType":"article","parentId":19761,"uid":1789,"contents":"<a href=\"/article/item_id-398459#\" title=\"/article/item_id-398459#\">[quote][/quote]</a><br>\n聖母是中國流行的俚語，指代那些任何情況都會以博愛之名要求人原諒和包容，卻往往流於偽善、為欺壓背書的人，並不是真的指甚麼女神。","date":"2020-06-01","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}